snippet.title: INSTANT SPORTS Paradise - Reveal Trailer (EN)
snippet.description:
INSTANT SPORTS Paradise makes the sun shine bright on your family workouts! Travel to the other side of the planet and enjoy an experience of 1 to 4 local players, all on your cosy couch!

INSTANT SPORTS Paradise release this summer on Nintendo Switch, Xbox One and PlayStation 4 !

More information : https://www.justforgames.com/product/instant-sports-paradise/
